Package com.bws.jdistil.core.process.model

Class Summary
DeleteDataObject<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Deletes a data object using submitted information.
EditDataObject<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Retrieves information needed to add/edit a data object.
FilterCriteriaDefinition Creates a filter criteria object using parameter data contained in a given HTTP request and predefined value criterion definitions and order criteria definitions.
OrderCriterionDefinition Defines an order criterion based on a field ID and order direction.
SaveDataObject<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Saves a data object using submitted data.
SelectDataObjects<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Provides support for viewing and selecting data objects as values associated with another data object.
ValueCriterionDefinition Defines a value criterion definition based on a target field ID, operator field ID, default operatorvalue, field ID, and default field value.
ViewDataObjects<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Retrieves a list of data objects and stores them into the request attributes.
